" clean stacktraces
nnoremap <Leader>st :<C-U>g/^\tat.*\.java.*/d<CR>:<C-U>g/^\tat.*(Unknown Source).*/d<CR>:<C-U>g/^\tat.*(Native Method).*/d<CR>
"noremap <Leader>st :<C-U>g/^\tat .*\(\.java:[0-9]\+\\|(Native Method)\\|(Unknown Source)\).*/d<CR>

" Dash lookup word under cursor
